List-available-ips dedibox resources.

USAGE:
  scw dedibox san list-available-ips [arg=value ...]

ARGS:
  rpn-san-id   RPN SAN ID
  [type]       Filter by IP type (server | rpnv2_subnet) (unknown | server_ip | rpnv2_subnet)

FLAGS:
  -h, --help   help for list-available-ips

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -B, --beta             Enable beta mode
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use
